      "writtenOn": "2019-09-26T20:23:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e For a build containing many swarming tasks, each swarming task will have their own Invocation, and their Invocations are included in the build\u0027s Invocation by Inclusion. Right?\n\nRight\n\n\u003e \n\u003e And included_invocation is the same as the child invocation\u0027s name.\n\nhm, no. Note that task invocation does not know who includes it. The build knows: inclusions belong to the build. Each inclusion edge specifies the task invocation in this field.",
